<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <title>Simple HTML Page</title>

    <style>

        body {

            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;

            margin: 20px;

            background-color: #f0f0f0;

            color: #333;

            line-height: 1.6;

            padding: 20px;

        }


        h1 {

            color: #21148f;

            text-align: center;

            font-size: 2.5em;

        }


        p {

            color: #c92b2b;

        }

    </style>

    <link href="/manifest.json" rel="manifest">

    <link rel="icon" href="/images/pwaicon.png">

    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/images/pwaicon.png">

    <script src="/sw.js"></script>

</head>

<body>

    <h1>Welcome to My Simple HTML Page</h1>

    <p>This is a basic example of an HTML page with some styling.</p>

    <table border="0">

        <tr>

            <th>Picture</th>

            <th>Description</th>

        </tr>

        <tr>

            <td><img src="/images/rvcelogo.jpg" width="100px" height="100px"></td>

            <td>RVCE Logo</td>

        </tr>

        <tr>

            <td><img src="/images/pwaicon.png" width="100px" height="100px"></td>

            <td>PWA ICON</td>

        </tr>

    </table>

inside the html page with manifest

</body>

</html>
